examples.en: This is allowed by the law.
He allowed himself no meat.
Smoking is not allowed.
It had been allowed for law.
How much time are we allowed?
We were allowed two tries each.
No refunds or exchanges are allowed.
The judge allowed the evidence.
We allowed the children to go to the park.
The school is not allowed to discriminate.
The speaker allowed the objection.
Women were not allowed in the club.
No one was allowed to leave their post.
We allowed them no respite.
'Am I allowed in?' 'Naturally.'
Smut is not allowed in this house.
They are allowed an hour for lunch.
His speech overran the time allowed.
We allowed for the difference in age.
Are dictionaries allowed in the exam?
She was allowed home on February 6th.
The audience is not allowed backstage.
No cars are allowed beyond this point.
They allowed just one vote per person.
The guard allowed the visitor to pass.
Women are not allowed to enter the mosque.
No cars are allowed on the island.
You're not allowed to chew gum in class.
Admission is seldom allowed to outsiders.
Spectators were not allowed past the bar.
